sfField.formula: IF(CONTAINS( SLA_Status__c , "Overdue") || CONTAINS( SLA_Status__c , "Missed"),IF(NOT(ISBLANK(ClosedDate)),DATEVALUE(ClosedDate) - DATEVALUE(CreatedDate), TODAY() - DATEVALUE(CreatedDate)), NULL)

IF(SLA_Status__c = "Overdue", "Overdue", IF(AND (ISPICKVAL(Status, "New"), AND((TODAY()-DATEVALUE(CreatedDate)) >= 0.50*( Incap311__Service_Type_Version__r.Incap311__SLA__c ), (TODAY()-DATEVALUE(CreatedDate)) <= 0.80*(Incap311__Service_Type_Version__r.Incap311__SLA__c ))), "50", IF(AND(NOT(ISPICKVAL(Status, "Closed")),(TODAY()-DATEVALUE(CreatedDate) >= 0.80*(Incap311__Service_Type_Version__r.Incap311__SLA__c ))), "80", IF(AND(NOT(ISPICKVAL(Status, "Closed")),(TODAY() = DATEVALUE( Incap311__Expected_Date_Time__c ))), TEXT(TODAY()) , 'NULL')) ) )
if( IsClosed, if ( ClosedDate <= Incap311__Expected_Date_Time__c , 'Met', 'Missed' ), if ( Now() <= Incap311__Expected_Date_Time__c , 'Open', 'Overdue' ))
